						               													<description>Scott Pilgrim Miniatures the World! is a competitive board game where one team takes on the role of Scott and the other good guys to fight against The League of Evil Exes. The action takes place on a pop-up board with large miniatures, custom dice, and 3D constructible objects for smashing and throwing!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this miniatures combat game, you'll go head to head either as Scott and his friends or as an Evil Ex. You'll roll dice and take actions including: moving, using a basic attack (punching or kicking), recovering health, picking up and throwing objects, or using one of a character's special abilities pulled right from the pages of the Scott Pilgrim graphic novels.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Deal damage to your opponent and knock them out by reducing them to 0 health. Scott and his friends win if they knock out the Evil Ex, but they'll have quite the challenge! The Bad Guys win if all the Good Guys are knocked out.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
